data.description: * Offering brand new carpet upstairs and $5,000 dollars towards buying the rate down for a buyer with a competitive offer* Priced BELOW appraised value! Welcome to 5700 Pelican Hills in Schertz, TX! Nestled in a secluded cul-de-sac, this spacious two-story gem is a true find. Located just off 35 past 1103, this home offers both convenience and comfort.  Step inside and be greeted by the stunning renovation featuring beautiful wood tile throughout the living areas, giving the home a modern and luxurious feel. The fully renovated kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting, sleek countertops, a gorgeous backsplash, and plenty of storage space.    The main floor also showcases the fully renovated master bath and new carpet in the master bedroom, creating a serene retreat for relaxation. The primary bedroom, conveniently located downstairs, offers privacy and convenience.    Upstairs, you'll discover a versatile loft space that can be tailored to your needs - whether it's an office for remote work, a playroom for the kids, or a cozy media room for movie nights.    But the delights don't stop inside - step outside to the spacious backyard, perfect for entertaining! Enjoy outdoor gatherings, BBQs, and relaxation in this inviting outdoor oasis.    Minutes away from HEB, EVO Entertainment, and a variety of restaurants and retail stores along 35, you'll have everything you need within reach.    Don't miss the opportunity to make 5700 Pelican Hills your new home.
